        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Why AI Agents:</strong> Tasks are well-defined with clear input/output
          specifications, validation against schemas provides strong error detection, and
          single-pass processing suffices. LLM's natural language understanding and structured
          output generation directly address the problem.
