          <strong>Key Trends:</strong> Shift from simple UI building to "Frontend Ops" and complex
          application architecture. Heavy reliance on component-based frameworks and edge rendering.
          <br />
          <strong>Dominant Stack:</strong> React (remains king), Vue.js, TypeScript, Next.js, Tailwind CSS.
